{"tid":2108432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同志另結新歡主動付分手費 「主人」疑感不忿再索款被控","createTime":"2020-07-14T13:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T13:57:50.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6c0bd1c7044adb1b2f7b3fa0d4d8404d9615c2","tid":2108432,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"男同志另結新歡，向交往半年的同志友人提出不再聯絡，並自願付出3,000元作補償，惟友人疑繼續索取金錢。事主恐怕早前傳給友人的下體照片會在網上公開，報警處理。友人終被控勒索罪，案件今在區域法院開審。事主供稱，兩人交往時他以「主人」稱呼被告，並自稱為「狗」。至他另結新歡，起初由他提議付錢分手，惟轉賬後，被告仍威脅將二人對話紀錄放上同志交友網，「畀你條仔見識下你之前點樣溝仔」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200713/COAK5RPBXOCCRPQOOQX2E4DTWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FCOAK5RPBXOCCRPQOOQX2E4DTWY%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=9bf0ded8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200713%2FCOAK5RPBXOCCRPQOOQX2E4DTWY%2F&h=f19c5468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200713/COAK5RPBXOCCRPQOOQX2E4DTWY/</a>"}]}